title: Urban Fresh
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Organic, Raw, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Plant-food cuisine created to aid health, since summer 2013. Offers salads with choice of oil-free dressing, wraps and sandwiches, desserts, soups, smoothies and juices. Daily specials, grab-n-go. Also hosts cooking classes and educating the community on the benefits of a plant-based lifestyle. July 2015 owner reported it's re-opened.
